# Weather Prediction Analysis using Machine Learning

## Project Overview
This project uses Machine Learning to analyze historical temperature data and predict future weather trends using Linear Regression.

It visualizes observed temperature patterns, prediction trends, and future forecasting with professional graphical analysis.

---

## Features
- Historical Temperature Analysis
- Future Temperature Prediction
- Professional Data Visualization
- Trend Detection using Linear Regression
- Forecast Highlighting with Prediction Marker

---

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Scikit-learn
- Linear Regression

---

